                                                      </p>
                                                                    <p>
                                                        <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/search/publication?q=Securing Machine Learning: Understanding Adversarial Attacks and Bias Mitigation" class="rg-button" target="_blank/"><strong>ResearchGate</strong></a>
